    "Short Description": "Auntie Ming of Kelly Hair Salon has been cutting hair since her twenties, taking her talents from China to 19 Pell St over two decades ago. This corner salon is a staple of the neighborhood, as many customers congregate here for the community in addition, of course, to the great haircuts.",
